channel.title: Gunz, BF macro
channel.description:
If you dont know what im talking about, this is what i mean:
when i press "t" i want it to press "space-w-w-leftclick-rightclick" when i press "g" i want it to press "space-s-s-leftclick-rightclick" when i press "f" i want it to press "space-a-a-leftclick-rightclick" when i press "h" i want it to press "space-d-d-leftclick-rightclick"
Thanks if you can.
